rong>:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Every spine irrespective of the starting slide is seen</li>\n<li>Earlier the spines covered an image by overlapping it. This issue has been resolved</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/sdimage.png\"><img class=\"size-large wp-image-17011 aligncenter\" src=\"http://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/sdimage-580x336.png\" alt=\"Classic lens\" width=\"580\" height=\"336\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>Other bug fixes</strong>:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>The &#8216;Scale proportionally and do not crop&#8217; option works just right now. The aspect ratio of all images is now maintained</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/scale-proportionlly-do-not-crop.png\"><img class=\"size-large wp-image-17013 aligncenter\" src=\"http://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/scale-proportionlly-do-not-crop-580x346.png\" alt=\"scale-proportionlly-do-not-crop\" width=\"580\" height=\"346\" /></a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>js error in the admin panel fixed for all SlideDeck pages</li>\n</ul>\n<p>These are the recent updates. More addons and updates are on the way.</p>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<h2>Buy SlideDeck3 and get all of this , and more.</h2>\n</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.slidedeck.com/pricing/\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-16026\" src=\"http://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/get_slidedeck.png\" alt=\"Get SlideDeck3\" width=\"272\" height=\"60\" /></a></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<p>Already have SlideDeck3? Update to the latest version <a href=\"https://www.slidedeck.com/my-account/\">here</a></p>\n<p>Need help with anything or have an out-of-box idea for SlideDeck?</p>\n<p>Shout out. We are all ears. ( <a href=\"mailto:support@slidedeck.com\" target=\"_blank\">support@slidedeck.com</a> )</p>\n</div>\n<br/><br/><a href=\"http://www.slidedeck.com/pricing/?utm_source=feed_ad&utm_medium=b