http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:3435:\"<p><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"><strong>Do you agree ?</strong></span></p>\n<p>&#8230;Your Sliders occupy the most premium space on your website</p>\n<p>&#8230;As soon as someone lands on your website, they are immediately drawn to your slider</p>\n<p>&#8230;So the best position to place your Call-To-Action buttons is on your slider !</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>CREATE CRAZY EFFECTIVE CALL-TO-ACTIONs THAT CONVERT</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">With a strong, clear Call-To-Action, you can &#8211;<br />\n&#8211; Engage with your visitors<br />\n&#8211; Create an efficient workflow<br />\n&#8211; Point your visitors in the right direction<br />\n&#8211; Boost your conversion rate</p>\n<p><strong>OPTIMIZE YOUR CTA BUTTONS FOR CONVERSION</strong></p>\n<p>SlideDeck3&#8217;s Lead Generation Addon helps you track the number of clicks on each Call-To-Action button, so keep tweaking your Call-To-Action Button to see which one gets most clicks !</p>\n<p><strong>SLIDEDECK3 NOW COMES WITH A LEAD GENERATION ADDON</strong></p>\n<p>This Lead Generation Addon will help you &#8211;</p>\n<p>1. Create simple Call To Action (CTA)  for your sliders and link them to your landing page<br />\n2. Track your Click-Through-Rate, find out which slide was clicked the most</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">SlideDeck3&#8217;s new release <strong>Version 3.3</strong> includes this add-on (with all licenses).</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.slidedeck.com/pricing/\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-16026 aligncenter\" src=\"http://www.slidedeck.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/get_slidedeck.png\" alt=\"Get SlideDeck3\" width=\"272\" height=\"60\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em><strong>P.S. </strong></em>If you have SlideDeck3 already, simply <a href=\"http://www.slidedeck.com/my-account/?utm_source=SlideDeck&amp;utm_campaign=682ad7537